MasterChannelService -> UIAdapterService: Depends on
MasterChannelService -> ChannelService: Depends on
MasterChannelService -> DynamicChannelService: Depends on

// End point
registerServices -> End [shape: oval, icon: stop-circle]
```

This setup ensures that all services are registered and can be easily retrieved from a central location, adhering to the Service Locator design pattern.

