2. **Test Case**: The test case registers two services (`CircularServiceA` and `CircularServiceB`) that depend on each other, creating a circular dependency. The test then expects the `waitFor` method to throw an error indicating a circular dependency.

By running this test, you can verify that the system correctly detects and handles circular dependencies.

